name: allItems
description: Returns all slotted tabs and their subTabs in a flattened array. The order of tabs is depth-first. For example, given the following slotted elements: ... ... ... ... Calling allItems on this TabContainer will return the instances in the following order: [ ui5-tab#First, ui5-tab#Nested, ui5-tab#Second, ui5-tab-separator#sep, ui5-tab#Third ]
